 <title>PSH-16-0080 - In the Matter of Personnel Security Hearing</title>
 <link>https://energy.gov/oha/downloads/psh-16-0080-matter-personnel-security-hearing</link>
 <description>&lt;a href=&quot;/oha/downloads/psh-16-0080-matter-personnel-security-hearing&quot; class=&quot;title-link&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;PSH-16-0080 - In the Matter of Personnel Security Hearing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  property=&quot;content:encoded&quot; class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;On February 9, 2017, an Administrative Judge issued a decision in which she found that an individual’s access authorization should be restored.  In June 2015, the Local Security Office (LSO) conducted a Personnel Security Interview (PSI) of the individual to address concerns about his Driving Under the Influence (DUI) arrest and his alcohol use.  In addition to the PSI, the LSO recommended a psychological evaluation of the individual by a DOE consultant psychologist (DOE psychologist) who opined that the individual suffers from Alcohol Use Disorder, Mild.  During the hearing, the individual acknowledged his 2015 DUI arrest and alcohol use and testified that he drank alcohol to deal with marital stress.  He asserted that he has abstained from alcohol for nine months and has no intention to drink alcohol in the future.  He also testified that he has completed a 20-hour DUI course, participated in outpatient counseling and is participating in an online Alcoholics Anonymous program.  The DOE psychologist opined that the individual has a good prognosis and has achieved rehabilitation and reformation.  The Administrative Judge therefore found that the individual has sufficiently resolved the DOE’s security concerns under Criteria H, J and L.  OHA Case No. PSH-16-0080 (Kimberly Jenkins-Chapman - Administrative Judge)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-download-files field-type-file field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;media-link-wrapper&quot; href=&quot;https://energy.gov/sites/prod/files/2017/02/f34/PSH-16-0080.pdf&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;filename&quot;&gt;PSH-16-0080.pdf&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;filesize&quot;&gt;(268.68 KB)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
