 <title>PSH-16-0083 - In the Matter of Personnel Security Hearing</title>
 <link>https://energy.gov/oha/downloads/psh-16-0083-matter-personnel-security-hearing</link>
 <description>&lt;a href=&quot;/oha/downloads/psh-16-0083-matter-personnel-security-hearing&quot; class=&quot;title-link&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;PSH-16-0083 - In the Matter of Personnel Security Hearing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  property=&quot;content:encoded&quot; class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;On January 31, 2017, an OHA Administrative Judge issued a decision in which he determined that an individual’s DOE access authorization should be restored.  The individual disclosed in a Questionnaire for National Security Positions that he submitted in 2015 that he had used marijuana on two occasions in 2010 while holding a DOE security clearance.  However, the Administrative Judge found that several factors cited in the Adjudicative Guidelines provided mitigation of the concerns raised by the individual’s marijuana use in 2010.  Specifically, the Administrative Judge found that a sufficient time has passed since the last occurrence of his marijuana use, and that his marijuana use, which occurred only twice, was infrequent.  Accordingly, the Administrative Judge concluded that the individual’s marijuana use is highly unlikely to recur and, therefore, does not cast doubt upon the individual’s present reliability, trustworthiness, or good judgment.  Therefore, the Administrative Judge found that the individual had resolved the security concerns.  OHA Case No. PSH-16-0083 (Steven L. Fine - Administrative Judge)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-download-files field-type-file field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;media-link-wrapper&quot; href=&quot;https://energy.gov/sites/prod/files/2017/02/f34/PSH-16-0083.pdf&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;filename&quot;&gt;PSH-16-0083.pdf&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;filesize&quot;&gt;(105.85 KB)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
