 <title>PSH-16-0078 - In the Matter of Personnel Security Hearing</title>
 <link>https://energy.gov/oha/downloads/psh-16-0078-matter-personnel-security-hearing</link>
 <description>&lt;a href=&quot;/oha/downloads/psh-16-0078-matter-personnel-security-hearing&quot; class=&quot;title-link&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;PSH-16-0078 - In the Matter of Personnel Security Hearing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  property=&quot;content:encoded&quot; class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;On January 23, 2017, an Administrative Judge (AJ) issued a decision in which he concluded that an individual’s access authorization should not be restored. In reaching this determination, the AJ found that the individual had not resolved security concerns under Guidelines G and J of the Revised Adjudicative Guidelines for Determining Eligibility for Access to Classified Information. Under Guideline G, which relates to excessive alcohol consumption, the AJ concluded that the individual’s six months of responsible behavior regarding alcohol were insufficient to demonstrate rehabilitation or reformation from his alcohol use disorder, given the individual’s lengthy history of abusive drinking. Regarding Guideline J, which concerns illegal behavior, the AJ found that since the individual’s chances of returning to an abusive pattern of drinking were unacceptably high, his chances of engaging in future alcohol-related illegal activity were also unacceptably high. Consequently, the AJ found that the individual’s security clearance should not be restored.  OHA Case No. Case No. PSH-16-0078 (Robert B. Palmer - Administrative Judge)     &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-download-files field-type-file field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;media-link-wrapper&quot; href=&quot;https://energy.gov/sites/prod/files/2017/02/f34/PSH-16-0078.pdf&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;filename&quot;&gt;PSH-16-0078.pdf&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;filesize&quot;&gt;(55.47 KB)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
