<item>
 <title>PSH-16-0081  - In the Matter of Personnel Security Hearing</title>
 <link>https://energy.gov/oha/downloads/psh-16-0081-matter-personnel-security-hearing</link>
 <description>&lt;a href=&quot;/oha/downloads/psh-16-0081-matter-personnel-security-hearing&quot; class=&quot;title-link&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;PSH-16-0081  - In the Matter of Personnel Security Hearing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  property=&quot;content:encoded&quot; class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt; &lt;p&gt;On January 9, 2017, an OHA Administrative Judge issued a decision in which she determined that an individual’s access authorization should be restored.  In reaching this determination, the Administrative Judge found that the individual had resolved the security concerns arising from his unpaid debts and his failure to file and pay his 2013, 2014, and 2015 Federal income taxes.  The individual and his mother testified that he is now current on all his debts and has filed his delinquent tax returns.  They both testified that the unpaid debts arose during his marriage, when his wife was paying their bills.  She developed a medical problem and became addicted to pain medication, often failing to pay the bills.  As to the tax returns, they separated in 2013 and divorced in 2014.  Although the individual was paying child support, his ex-wife claimed the children on her tax returns, forcing him into a situation where he was unsure what to do.  Therefore, he did not file the tax returns.  Due to the individual’s mitigation of the claims, the Administrative Judge found that the individual had resolved the Criterion L concerns.  OHA Case No. PSH-16-0081 (Janet R. H. Fishman,  Administrative Judge)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-download-files field-type-file field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;media-link-wrapper&quot; href=&quot;https://energy.gov/sites/prod/files/2017/01/f34/PSH-16-0081.pdf&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;filename&quot;&gt;PSH-16-0081.pdf&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;filesize&quot;&gt;(348.33 KB)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
